wikipedia_page.main:
Kathryn Lane  (born 27 February 1995) is an English international field hockey player who played as a defender for England..She plays club hockey in the Women's England Hockey League Premier Division for Clifton Robinsons.
Lane has also played for Beeston and Leicester.
